criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with histologically confirmed diagnosis of Crohn disease (CD) or Ulcerative
             colitis (UC) in the last 6 months and undergoing followup colonoscopy.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  (a) prior proctocolectomy;

          -  (b) presence of IBD extraintestinal manifestation;

          -  (c) treatment with antibiotics in the last 60 days;

          -  (d) extensive surgical resection;

          -  (e) presence of stoma.
